# Project Overview

<img src="images/logo.png" alt="Tennis Australia Logo" class="logo"/>

- **Objective**: Develop predictive models to recommend the best racquets based on player data.
- **Tools**: Python, R, Machine Learning algorithms.
- **Outcome**: Data-driven insights for personalized racquet selection.

---

# Data Collection

<img src="images/logo.png" alt="Tennis Australia Logo" class="logo"/>

- **Player Data**: Historical performance, playing style, and physical characteristics.
- **Data Sources**: Tennis Australiaâ€™s player database, match statistics, surveys.

---

# Methodology

<img src="images/logo.png" alt="Tennis Australia Logo" class="logo"/>

1. Data Preprocessing
   - Cleaning and normalizing data
   - Feature engineering
2. Model Development
   - Machine learning models (e.g., Random Forest, SVM)
   - Model validation and tuning
3. Predictive Analysis
   - Predicting optimal racquet type for different player profiles

